original_title: I Am A Cuck - Tim Heidecker vs. Sam Hyde
overview: ON THE EVE OF THE 2016 PRESIDENTIAL ELECTION alternative comedian, Tim Heidecker, decides to start an online call-in show, Office Hours, so he can talk seriously to his fans. Meanwhile, a young upstart in the comedy world, Sam Hyde gets his big break on the Adult Swim network. When his alt right tweets inflame an all-out war between the two men's fanbases on social media, Heidecker has no option but to pick sides...
title: I Am A Cuck - Tim Heidecker vs. Sam Hyde
